  ('medical-tech-moex-06468', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-108-9168e375', 'sub-medical-tech-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '20歲的王小姐每個月月經量都很多，最近開始覺得臉色蒼白、易喘、指甲變薄、易斷，舌苔薄且愛吃冰塊。 有關王小姐的檢驗數據，下列那個最不可能出現？', '["Hemoglobin 6.8 g/dL", "Ferritin 1.1 mg/dL", "MCV 57 fL", "RDW 11.5%"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:16:27+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "b37fe12bd181", "answer_pdf_sha1": "aadb45b02238", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "108100", "c": "308", "s": "22", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "臨床血液學與血庫學", "year": "108", "exam_name": "108年第二次專技人員高等考試醫師考試分階段考試（第一階段）、牙醫師藥師考試分階段考試、醫事檢驗師、醫事放射師、物理治療師、職能治療師、呼吸...", "original_question_number": 51, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
