  ('medical-tech-moex-06475', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-108-9168e375', 'sub-medical-tech-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列有關自體免疫溶血性貧血（AIHA）的敘述，何者正確？', '["冷型AIHA的抗體大多屬於IgG抗體，IgG附著於紅血球，抗體於4℃與紅血球起反應", "冷凝集素病為冷型AIHA，因為IgG附著於紅血球上，IgG抗體對抗紅血球表面的I或i抗原", "溫型AIHA的抗體大多屬於IgM抗體，IgM附著於紅血球，抗體於37℃與紅血球起反應", "溫型AIHA的DAT（direct antiglobulin test）為陽性反應"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:16:27+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "b37fe12bd181", "answer_pdf_sha1": "aadb45b02238", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "108100", "c": "308", "s": "22", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "臨床血液學與血庫學", "year": "108", "exam_name": "108年第二次專技人員高等考試醫師考試分階段考試（第一階段）、牙醫師藥師考試分階段考試、醫事檢驗師、醫事放射師、物理治療師、職能治療師、呼吸...", "original_question_number": 58, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('medical-tech-moex-06476', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-108-9168e375', 'sub-medical-tech-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列有關megaloblastic anemia檢驗結果的敘述，何者錯誤？', '["骨髓有核紅血球數目減少", "周邊血中紅血球數目減少", "血清total bilirubin上升", "Serum iron及ferritin增加"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:16:27+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "b37fe12bd181", "answer_pdf_sha1": "aadb45b02238", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "108100", "c": "308", "s": "22", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "臨床血液學與血庫學", "year": "108", "exam_name": "108年第二次專技人員高等考試醫師考試分階段考試（第一階段）、牙醫師藥師考試分階段考試、醫事檢驗師、醫事放射師、物理治療師、職能治療師、呼吸...", "original_question_number": 59, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('medical-tech-moex-06477', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-108-9168e375', 'sub-medical-tech-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列有關vitamin B 之敘述，何者錯誤？ 12', '["存在於動物性製品，而不存在於蔬菜、穀物或水果中", "在小腸迴腸段吸收，且需要intrinsic factor之輔助", "於肝門脈循環或體循環中，都必須和血漿中的haptocorrin（transcobalamin I）結合", "身體儲存量比每日需求量高出許多，短期的缺乏並不會立即造成顯著的影響"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:16:27+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "b37fe12bd181", "answer_pdf_sha1": "aadb45b02238", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "108100", "c": "308", "s": "22", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "臨床血液學與血庫學", "year": "108", "exam_name": "108年第二次專技人員高等考試醫師考試分階段考試（第一階段）、牙醫師藥師考試分階段考試、醫事檢驗師、醫事放射師、物理治療師、職能治療師、呼吸...", "original_question_number": 60, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL)
